column5:
11 pages, 6 figures, 1 table; to be published in Optics Express;
  revisions include adjustment of some citations, additions to section 2, and
  added information in table 1

column11:
  In this work we present our work in developing a software verification tool
for llvm-code - Lodin - that incorporates both explicit-state model checking,
statistical model checking and symbolic state model checking algorithms.
